      "value": "<p>RenderMan for Katana supports cameras created with a CameraCreate node or imported from an Alembic file. You can control various camera effects through the attributes on the camera using PrmanCameraSettings.  Supported camera effects include:</p><ul class=\"childpages-macro conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"cd45dfc3-b861-4ff7-9522-c7711ed264ff\" data-macro-id=\"7f4298ab-dd6d-4d73-aa90-31ee67a1b56a\" data-macro-name=\"children\"><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFK27/pages/546178644/Motion+Blur+in+Katana\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546178644\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Motion Blur in Katana</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFK27/pages/546178680/Display+Sample+Filters+in+Katana\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546178680\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Display &amp; Sample Filters in Katana</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFK27/pages/546178709/Camera+Settings+in+Katana\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546178709\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Camera Settings in Katana</a></li></ul>"
